00:42:02.000 --> 00:42:04.800
Lahat ng nasa
Anhui Tea Merchants' Association

00:42:05.150 --> 00:42:06.480
humihingi ng tawad.

00:42:06.480 --> 00:42:07.760
Hindi ko ito matatanggap, Old Master Hu.

00:42:07.760 --> 00:42:08.620
hindi ko talaga kaya.

00:42:09.070 --> 00:42:09.870
Please bumangon ka na.

00:42:12.760 --> 00:42:14.620
Mas matanda ka pa sa nanay ko.

00:42:14.840 --> 00:42:17.100
Hindi ko siguro matatanggap ang ganoong kilos.

00:42:17.590 --> 00:42:18.190
lahat,

00:42:19.000 --> 00:42:19.840
kung ikaw talaga

00:42:19.840 --> 00:42:21.100
nais kong sundin ang aking pamumuno,

00:42:21.360 --> 00:42:23.190
then please makinig ka sa sasabihin ko.

00:42:23.190 --> 00:42:24.790
Pakiusap, maupo na ang lahat.

00:42:25.070 --> 00:42:25.870
Old Master Hu,

00:42:26.360 --> 00:42:28.020
mangyaring umupo sa upuan ng karangalan.

00:42:36.550 --> 00:42:37.320
Ilabas mo.

00:42:39.960 --> 00:42:40.890
Huwag kang tulala.

00:42:50.480 --> 00:42:51.110
lahat,

00:42:52.400 --> 00:42:54.730
Ako ay mayabang at walang galang sa Anhui

00:42:54.960 --> 00:42:56.490
at nasaktan si Old Master Hu.

00:42:57.400 --> 00:42:58.510
Ngayon, si Old Master Hu

00:42:58.510 --> 00:42:59.800
gustong humingi ng tawad sa akin,

00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:00.400
at gusto ko rin humingi ng tawad

00:43:00.400 --> 00:43:01.700
sa kabuuan

00:43:01.840 --> 00:43:02.510
Samahan ng mga Mangangalakal ng Anhui Tea.

